    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1997 Porsche 911 Carrera (993), the final evolution of the air-cooled flat-six. This specimen features the 3.6L powerplant equipped with the VarioRam induction system, providing optimized volumetric efficiency across the entire power band. The G50 6-speed manual transaxle remains precise, with firm detents and no evidence of synchro degradation. All factory cosmoline is present on the undercarriage, and the heat exchangers show no signs of thermal stress or oxidation. The multi-link LSA rear axle preserves perfect kinematics, ensuring the chassis remains settled under high lateral G-loads. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically preserved, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
