    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This car has been fastidiously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in an exterior finish that is absolutely flawless. The paint depth is consistent across every panel, treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that provides a mirror-like clarity and protection against the elements. There are no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the high-grade leather remains soft and matte, showing no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains intact. Every switch, dial, and digital interface operates with the crisp precision of a new vehicle. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It features a comprehensive service history documented from day one, with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The undercarriage and engine bay are pristine, free of any debris or fluid seepage. This vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 44900.0,
