    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) in mint condition. This example features the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine producing 315 hp, utilizing VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is delivered via a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec McPherson struts and a multi-link rear suspension, while braking is handled by four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers. Mechanically flawless, the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic retrofit, and the RMS remains bone dry. The DME report shows zero over-revs in high ranges, confirming a life of meticulous operation. This is a turn-key performance machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
